Semantic seed status
====================

COMPLETE for the design-inventory contract:

- Every DOT solid/named/axiom vertex has a seed entity (id + kind).
- Every solid DOT edge has a preferred typed seed arrow.
- Named joins use structured classifier_application / classifier_tower /
  pullback definitions (no “Imported from DOT” leftovers).
- correspondence.json targets are semantic_seed entity ids.
- `just seed-dot` writes the presentation DOT from the seed (factory/viz).
- One-tower Magmas: AdditiveMagmas = Magmas.Additive via clf.magmas.additive;
  additive semigroups/monoids/groups/abelian groups reuse Magmas law
  classifiers with along=additive_operation (no clf.additive_magmas.* family).
- Named-join parsing uses longest-prefix hosts (Magmas.Additive.Associative).

Property/structure/stuff is not stored on classifiers — compute from the leg.
Aut/GL/Pic-style values remain construction_value aliases.
